<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
html { background: #ffffff; }
body {
  width: 720pt; height: 405pt; margin: 0; padding: 0;
  background: #F4F6F6;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  display: flex;
}
.header {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 60pt;
  background: #2E4053;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding-left: 40pt;
}
.header h1 {
  color: #FFFFFF;
  font-size: 22pt;
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.content {
  margin-top: 80pt;
  margin-left: 60pt;
  margin-right: 60pt;
}
.speed-note {
  color: #E67E22;
  font-size: 14pt;
  margin: 0 0 20pt 0;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.section-box {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border-left: 5pt solid #E67E22;
  padding: 12pt 20pt;
  margin-bottom: 12pt;
  border-radius: 4pt;
}
.section-title {
  color: #E67E22;
  font-size: 16pt;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin: 0 0 8pt 0;
}
.market-list {
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 16pt;
}
.market-list li {
  color: #2C3E50;
  font-size: 12pt;
  margin: 4pt 0;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
  <h1>票据打印机（高速）</h1>
</div>
<div class="content">
  <p class="speed-note">打印速度：160mm/s以上</p>
  <div class="section-box">
    <p class="section-title">58mm</p>
    <ul class="market-list">
      <li>应用：商超、外卖</li>
      <li>市场：国内、东南亚</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section-box">
    <p class="section-title">80mm（切刀）</p>
    <ul class="market-list">
      <li>应用：商超</li>
      <li>市场：欧美</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
